'''麦肯锡·杰德·维加'''（{{lang-en|Makenzie Jade Vega}}，{{bd|1994年|2月10日}}）是一名[[美国|美国]][[女演员|女演员]]。她是演员[[阿丽夏·维加|阿丽夏·维加]]的妹妹。

== 生平和生涯 ==
麦肯锡·维加出生在[[加州|加州]][[洛杉矶市|洛杉矶市]]。她的父亲是哥伦比亚人。母亲吉娜·鲁之前是一名美国模特。<ref name="notitalian">{{Cite web|title = Alexa Forever|work = RE: Questions for Miss Alexa Vega|url = http://www.alexa-vega.com/forum-archive/questions-for-miss-alexa-vega.html#alexaethnicity|accessdate = August 20, 2006|quote = My father's side is Colombian (Bogota)... and I don't know why they said my mom was Italian. lol... She's not. My family and I were trying to figure out what my mom was, but we can only go back to 5 generations and they were all from Florida. haha. so .. Floridian? ahhah... my moms last name is French though.}}</ref><ref name="dlaima">{{Cite news|title = Ex-spy has price on head, ache in heart|publisher = Miami Herald|date = September 7, 2009|url = http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=MH&s_site=miami&p_multi=MH&p_theme=realcities&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=12B3F492E15ED4D8&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM|accessdate = March 8, 2011|quote = Alexa Vega 21 is his oldest daughter with former Miami model Gina Rue With about 40 films in her career Alexa is mostly known for her role in the Spy Kids ...}}</ref><ref name="FilmReference">[http://www.filmreference.com/film/84/Alexa-Vega.html "Alexa Vega Biography"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.filmreference.com/film/84/Alexa-Vega.html |date=20170926235913 }}.</ref>

5岁的时候，维加就已经是The [[吉娜·戴维斯|Geena Davis]] Show的常驻演员。2000年，她在The Family Man扮演了坎贝尔的早熟女儿安妮。<ref>"Annie's not much of a violin player, but she tries real hard. </ref>2001年， 维加在由[[文斯·沃恩|文斯·沃恩]]、[[強·法夫洛|強·法夫洛]]和[[芳姬·詹森|芳姬·詹森]]出演的电影Made中饰演克洛伊。2004年，他在恐怖电影《[[电锯惊魂|电锯惊魂]]》中扮演了劳伦斯·戈登和阿丽森·戈登的女儿戴安娜·戈登。<ref name="VanityFair">"It's Evening in America". </ref>她的下一步电影是与[[布鲁斯·威利斯|布鲁斯·威利斯]]一起出演的《[[罪恶之城|罪恶之城]]》。剧中，她扮演的是年轻时的Nancy Callahan。 随后她还在[[琳賽·蘿涵|林赛·罗翰]]与[[McFly|McFly]]出演的电影《[[幸運之吻|幸运之吻]]》中出演了Katy。她还在《[[X战警3：最后之战|X战警3：最后之战]]》中扮演了一名小女孩。目前，她正在参与茱莉安娜·瑪格里斯主演的[[CBS|CBS]]电视剧《[[傲骨贤妻|傲骨贤妻]]》的拍摄。剧中她饰演女主角艾丽西亚·弗洛瑞克（Alicia Florrick）的女儿格蕾丝·弗洛瑞克（Grace Florrick）。<span class="cx-segment" data-segmentid="59"></span>

